dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. "1804 J. Russell del. et sc." handwritten in pencil on map margin. "Engraved for the Compendious Geographical Dictionary"--top margin. Likely detached from: A compendious geographical dictionary, published London: Printed for W. Peacock and Sons, Salisbury-Square, Fleet-Street ; By C. Rickaby, Peterborough-Court, 1804. Shows place names and regional/kingdom names. Scale not given
